## **Evaluate SPF, DKIM, and DMARC Compliance**

This section focuses on detailed analysis and validation of SPF, DKIM, and DMARC headers. Each authentication mechanism is evaluated to determine its status, providing critical insights into the email’s legitimacy and adherence to security protocols.

